Package edu.cs3500.spreadsheets.model.cells

Interface Cell

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    EmptyCell, SimpleCell
    public interface Cell

    Represents a cell in a worksheet.

    A cell can do the following.
    • Evaluate itself given a model.
    • Accept a VexpVisitor Visitor for evaluating itself.
